From: Vicki Pfau <vi@endrift.com>
Date: Tue, 13 May 2025 15:59:48 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Input: xpad - add more controllers
Git-commit: f0d17942ea3edec191f1c0fc0d2cd7feca8de2f0
